quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,43,"Nafu shikhwaruma imbeli wuwo halali Abasatsa abakhwafimbulilanga obufimbuli. Kho, reebe abali nobwitsulili nikali mbu shimumanyile tawe."
  16,44,"Khubimanyisio bili habulafu nende Ebitabu. Ne khweshia amachelo kho winoosilie Abandu akeshibwa khubo, khobanyoole okhupaara."
  16,45,"Ne koo basuubilanga mbu bali nomulembe balia abakholanga ebifwanga mbu Nyasaye shiyetsa okhubasishia muliloba tawe nohomba shalabarerera eshinyasio nabo nibalamanyile tawe?"
  16,46,"Nohomba shalabatila khutsinjendo tsiabu eyi nende eyi, mana shibalanyala okhushila tawe?"
  16,47,"Nohomba mbu shalabahelesia eshinyasio muburii bwabu tawe? Toto Nyasaye wuwo ni Omuholo, Oweshisa muno."
  16,48,"Koo! Shibalolangakhwo buli bia Nyasaye yaloonga eshinikha shiabio shibotokhananga okhurula omukhono omulunji nende omukaata, ne biinamilanga Nyasaye nibihotselesiye."
  16,49,"Ne binamilanga Nyasaye bioosi bichendanga mwikulu nende khushialo, mutsisolo nende Abamalaika boosi, ne shibali abafuru tawe."
  16,50,"Baritsanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi owuli hekulu wabu, ne bakholanga eliabalomesibungwa."
  16,51,"Ne Nyasaye yaboola mbu: “Mulabakhwo nende nyasaye babili tawe. Ye ni Nyasaye mulala butswa yenyene. Kho murie butswa esie!”"
  16,52,"Ni ebibie ebili mwikulu nende mushialo, ne idini neyiyie buli lwoosi. Koo, muritsanga ulali Nyasaye tawe?"
  16,53,"Ne emikabo chioosi cha muli ninacho ni okhurula khu Nyasaye, mana amabii nikabanyoola, niye butswa owamulililanga."
  16,54,"Mana nabarusiliaho obubii obo, awo sa, omukanda mulala mwinywe kukakhula okhumutsokaasia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."